# <type>(<scope>): <short imperative subject, ≤72 chars>
#
# Types: feat, fix, refactor, docs, style, test, chore, perf, build
# Scopes (examples): ui, ui/dashboard, ui/sessions, api/nft, api/auth,
#                    auth, contracts, repo, deps, ci
#
# --- body (optional) ------------------------------------------------
# Wrap at 72. Explain *why* the change is made, not *what* changed
# (the diff shows what). Leave a blank line between subject and body.
#
# --- footer (optional) ----------------------------------------------
# Breaking changes: prefix with "BREAKING CHANGE: ...".
# Issue refs: "Closes #123" / "Refs #45".
# Do not add AI-attribution trailers — the commit-msg hook blocks them.
